    <title>New: BILL051(26) (Honolulu) — INTRO</title>
    <updated>2026-07-15T16:15:06+00:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://hnldoc.ehawaii.gov/hnldoc/measure/3792"/>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RELATING TO PARKING.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Requires the DTS Director to mark with a warning certain parking restricted areas along curbs within one-quarter mile of any public access to a hiking trail.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Latest action: Introduced.&lt;/p&gt;
